\section{什麼是 Altered Scale？}

Altered Scale（變化音階）：把一個屬九和弦可以變化的音都變化過\episodenumref{sec:ep42}，再把全部的音合在一起的音階。

\begin{lilypond}[quote,fragment,staffsize=16]
<<
  \new ChordNames {
    \override ChordNames.ChordName.font-family = #'roman
    \override ChordNames.ChordName.font-size = #0.85
    \chordmode {c1:9}
  }
  \relative c' {
    \override Staff.TimeSignature #'stencil = ##f
    \cadenzaOn
    \accidentalStyle piano
    c1 e g bes d
    \bar "|."
  }
>>
\end{lilypond}

$\rightarrow$ C Altered Scale

\begin{lilypond}[quote,fragment,staffsize=16]
\relative c' {
  \override Staff.TimeSignature #'stencil = ##f
  \cadenzaOn
  \accidentalStyle piano
  c1 des dis e ges gis bes c
  \bar "|."
}
\end{lilypond}

$=$ C$\sharp$ 旋律小音階，與 C Altered Scale 使用到的音完全相同

